descriptionHtml:
A great App shows a big list of fruits and vegetables including pictures and written names in English. The good thing is that it spell each fruit name or each vegetable name. Furthermore, App shows enlarged image for each fruit or vegetable you click on.
Name of fruits are shown and spelled when you click on fruit thumb. Name of vegetables are shown and spelled when you click on vegetable thumb.


👉 Vegetable Fruit App Features:
⭐ You can learn fruits and vegetables names.
⭐ Gallery of all fruits and vegetables clipart. including famous and strange fruits.
⭐ App shows fruits and vegetables list in small thumbs to make you move easily between items.
⭐ You can see fruits and vegetables pictures. If you click any fruit or vegetable you will see large image of fruits or vegetables.
⭐ This App provides you with fruits and vegetables online.
⭐ It includes strangest fruits.

Some of strange looking fruits are: elephant apple, star fruit, and buddha's hand. Some strange fruits lyrics such as: sycamore fig, and quince.
